      "weather": "Fine",
      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BETTY BONKERS (4) comes off an average performance last start when seventh at Temora over 330m behind Westside Bullet (19.65) in a Grade 5. Can atone. KING OF ASGARD (8) drawn the outside box and could get a clear run. Was below best last time when 8th and beaten 15 lengths at Temora (20.13). Goes very well at course and distance boasting three wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from six starts. Expected to give a good account. SHA'CARRI (1) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at this track over 320m behind Stay Tipsy (19.00) in a Grade 5. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Can do much better this time. SYCAMORE MISS (2) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
